<div class="para" label-module="para">是你多么温馨的目光</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">教我坚毅望着前路</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">叮嘱我跌倒不应放弃</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">没法解释怎可报尽亲恩</div>
